    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">The Universal Tool 10 Pocket Pink Tool Pouch is a great addition to any crafter or hobbyists tool supplies. Each pouch features 2 main pockets, 2 medium pockets, 6 small pockets and a steel hammer holder. The pouches themselves are constructed of heavy duty pink suede leather. The tool pouch features a metal tape clip for measuring tape as well as a tunnel that will fit a 3 inch wide belt (belt not included). Note: rivets may show natural sign of rest from the manufacturing process.</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">Deluxe Carpenter Tool Belt Pouch Heavy Duty Suede Leather Fits Hammer And Nails</h2>\n  <p>The Universal Tool 10 Pocket Pink Tool Pouch is a great addition to any crafter or hobbyists tool supplies. Each pouch features 2 main pockets, 2 medium pockets, 6 small pockets and a steel hammer holder. The pouches themselves are constructed of heavy duty pink suede leather.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li>10 Pockets</li>\n    <li>2 Main Pockets | 2 Medium Pockets | 6 Small Pockets | 1 Steel Hammer Holder</li>\n    <li>Metal Tape Clip for Holding Measuring Tape</li>\n    <li>Belt Tunnel Fits 3 inch Wide Belt (Belt Not Included)</li>\n    <li>Heavy Duty Suede Leather</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1000x1000/Tools/AS1101A-PNK_9_pocket_toolbelt_detail_01.jpg\" alt=\"The Universal Tool 10 Pocket Pink Tool Pouch is a great addition to any crafter or hobbyists tool supplies\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> HWK106PKTB</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 148312804630</li>\n    <li><strong>Size:</strong> Adjustable</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>The tool pouch features a metal tape clip for measuring tape as well as a tunnel that will fit a 3 inch wide belt (belt not included).</p>\n  <p>Note: rivets may show natural sign of rest from the manufacturing process.</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
